raspisump (2.0~a1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Version 2.0 alpha release
  * Migrated to pyproject.toml (PEP 517/518)
  * Migrated from hcsr04sensor to pinsource (lgpio, Raspberry Pi 5 compatible)
